{"tid":2101102,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日澳領導人就黨國安法令一國兩制大幅倒退表達重大關切","createTime":"2020-07-09T14:03:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T14:33:15.000Z","uid":21470,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"01ea6b5c6447e33dbeaee44de2f475d1f9df2f09","tid":2101102,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T14:03:53.000Z","msg":"日澳領導人就港區國安法表達重大關切<br />\n最後更新時間 2020-07-09 21:33<br />\n<br />\n日本首相安倍晉三同澳洲總理莫里森，舉行<del>視頻會談</del>視像會議，一致認為，中方制定港區國安法，令一國兩制大幅倒退，表達重大關切。安倍又對中國在東海和南海活動表示關注，獲莫里森支持，雙方同意就加強軍事聯合訓練的協定，開展談判。<br />\n<br />\n莫里森早前公布，會放寬港人工作簽證期限至5年，便利移民，中斷同香港的引渡安排，及呼籲澳洲公民要審慎前往香港，引起北京不滿，警告保留反制權利，一切後果由澳洲承擔。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2346288\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2346288&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjhfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=6b433c8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2346288</a>"},{"pid":"dfe873d12fcb52405cb78abb9a427420310a2c3b","tid":2101102,"uid":118082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T14:05:08.000Z","msg":"日本之前唔係話會幫手收人?"},{"pid":"88dfdff071dfa2a12ce91689890191212e1befd9","tid":2101102,"uid":335434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dfe873d12fcb52405cb78abb9a427420310a2c3b","tid":2101102,"uid":118082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T14:05:08.000Z","msg":"日本之前唔係話會幫手收人?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T14:07:16.000Z","msg":"日本想揀香港堆金融專業人材嚟收留<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ca04cb97fc66981dc3af67ce3846957c465e4d1","tid":2101102,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88dfdff071dfa2a12ce91689890191212e1befd9","tid":2101102,"uid":335434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dfe873d12fcb52405cb78abb9a427420310a2c3b","tid":2101102,"uid":118082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T14:05:08.000Z","msg":"日本之前唔係話會幫手收